<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net">
  <diagram name="Página-1" id="v4w0xNLlb51hintJ34AH">
    <mxGraphModel dx="4482" dy="-7966" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml predict_inprocess_onnx\ntitle Predict — In-Process + ONNX Backend\n\nskinparam sequenceMessageAlign center\nskinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true\nskinparam maxMessageSize 200\nskinparam ParticipantPadding 20\nskinparam BoxPadding 10\nskinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5\nskinparam roundcorner 5\nskinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #333333\nskinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #333333\nskinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #DAE8FC\nskinparam sequenceActorBorderColor #333333\nskinparam noteBorderColor #AAAAAA\nskinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFFFCC\n\nactor \&quot;Caller\&quot; as Caller\n\nbox \&quot;miia::client\&quot; #EAF4FB\n    participant \&quot;InferenceClient\&quot; as IC\n    participant \&quot;InProcessBackend\&quot; as IPB\nend box\n\nbox \&quot;miia::worker (in-process)\&quot; #EAF7EA\n    participant \&quot;InferenceEngine\&quot; as IE\n    participant \&quot;OnnxBackend\&quot; as OB\nend box\n\nbox \&quot;ONNX Runtime\&quot; #F5F0FF\n    participant \&quot;Ort::Session\&quot; as ORT\nend box\n\nnote over IC, IPB\n  **Sem gRPC — sem serialização proto**\n  client::Object passado diretamente\n  target == \&quot;inprocess\&quot; | \&quot;in_process\&quot; | \&quot;local\&quot;\nend note\n\n== Setup (já conectado) ==\n\nCaller -&gt; IC : predict(\\n  model_id : string,\\n  inputs : Object)\nactivate IC\n\nIC -&gt; IPB : predict(\\n  model_id : string,\\n  inputs : client::Object)\nactivate IPB\n\nnote right of IPB\n  Sem conversão proto.\n  Object passado direto\n  ao InferenceEngine.\nend note\n\nIPB -&gt; IE : predict(\\n  model_id : string,\\n  inputs : client::Object\\n) : InferenceResult\nactivate IE\n\nIE -&gt; IE : check_auto_unload()\n\nnote right of IE\n  Lock mutex_\n  backend* = models_[model_id].backend.get()\n  Unlock mutex_\n  Chama predict() fora do lock\nend note\n\nIE -&gt; OB : predict(\\n  inputs : client::Object\\n) : InferenceResult\nactivate OB\n\nOB -&gt; OB : Ort::MemoryInfo::CreateCpu(\\n  OrtArenaAllocator,\\n  OrtMemTypeDefault\\n)\n\nloop para cada input tensor (input_names_[i])\n    OB -&gt; OB : value_to_floats(\\n  inputs[name] : Value\\n) : vector&lt;float&gt;\n\n    note right of OB\n      Value::is_number() → {val}\n      Value::is_array()  → iterate\n      as_number() : double → float\n    end note\n\n    OB -&gt; OB : resolve_dynamic_shape(\\n  input_shapes_[i] : vector&lt;int64_t&gt;,\\n  data.size() : size_t,\\n  name : string\\n) : vector&lt;int64_t&gt;\n\n    OB -&gt; OB : Ort::Value::CreateTensor&lt;float&gt;(\\n  mem_info,\\n  data.data() : float*,\\n  data.size(),\\n  shape.data(),\\n  shape.size()\\n) : Ort::Value\nend\n\nOB -&gt; ORT : session_-&gt;Run(\\n  RunOptions{nullptr},\\n  input_name_ptrs[] : const char**,\\n  input_tensors[] : Ort::Value*,\\n  n_inputs : size_t,\\n  output_name_ptrs[] : const char**,\\n  n_outputs : size_t\\n) : vector&lt;Ort::Value&gt;\nactivate ORT\n\nnote right of ORT\n  Execução do grafo ONNX\n  CPU (ou CUDA se enable_gpu_)\n  ORT_ENABLE_EXTENDED optimization\n  IntraOp threads = num_threads_\nend note\n\nORT --&gt; OB : vector&lt;Ort::Value&gt;\ndeactivate ORT\n\nloop para cada output tensor\n    OB -&gt; OB : tensor.GetTensorTypeAndShapeInfo()\\n→ count : size_t\n    OB -&gt; OB : tensor.GetTensorMutableData&lt;float&gt;()\\n→ ptr : const float*\n    OB -&gt; OB : floats_to_value(\\n  ptr : float*,\\n  count : size_t\\n) : client::Value\n    note right of OB\n      count == 1 → Value{double}\n      count &gt;  1 → Value{Array}\n    end note\nend\n\nOB -&gt; OB : metrics_.record(time_ms, true)\nOB -&gt; OB : touch()\n\nOB --&gt; IE : InferenceResult {\\n  success: true,\\n  outputs: client::Object,\\n  inference_time_ms: double,\\n  error_message: \&quot;\&quot;\\n}\ndeactivate OB\n\nIE --&gt; IPB : InferenceResult\ndeactivate IE\n\nIPB -&gt; IPB : result.success = r.success\\nresult.inference_time_ms = r.inference_time_ms\\nresult.outputs = move(r.outputs)\n\nIPB --&gt; IC : PredictionResult {\\n  success: bool,\\n  outputs: client::Object,\\n  inference_time_ms: double\\n}\ndeactivate IPB\n\nIC --&gt; Caller : PredictionResult\ndeactivate IC\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="OFugE89OlIWmUVSY5UGE-4">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="2172" width="1330" x="-1422" y="9698" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
